video.title: Pajanimals
video.synopsis: From the comfort of their bedroom, the Pajanimals puppets explore a larger world through imaginary adventures, accompanied by friendships and songs.

episodes.synopsis: Sweetpea Sue can't wait for pancakes on Saturday, but Mom decides to make waffles instead; Sweetpea is scared and wants to sleep in Mom and Dad's bed.
episodes.title: House of Pancakes / Missing Mom and Dad

episodes.synopsis: It's Mom's birthday, and Apollo feels his present for her isn't good enough; Cowbella has been a bit bossy lately and wants everyone to listen to her.
episodes.title: Present for Mom / Queen for a Night

episodes.synopsis: Apollo is disappointed that he keeps losing every race; Sweetpea Sue is afraid of octopi, so the Pajanimals take her to the sea to meet Ellie Octopus.
episodes.title: Winning Isn't Everything / An Octopus Hug

episodes.synopsis: Squacky is so excited about going to the movies tomorrow that he has trouble sleeping; Sweetpea Sue gets angry when Cowbella gets paint on Daisy Puff.
episodes.title: Super Squacky / I'm Sorry, Really Sorry

episodes.synopsis: The Pajanimals celebrate Sweetpea Sue's birthday; Squacky's blankie has to be washed overnight, and now he doesn't know what to snuggle with.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday Sweetpea Sue / Blankie in the Laundry

episodes.synopsis: The Pajanimals are going to be taught how to play baseball tomorrow, and Apollo's nervous he won't do well; Cowbella doesn't want to take a bath.
episodes.title: Try & Try Again / No Bath for Me

episodes.synopsis: Apollo and Cowbella both like purple but don't like sharing the same color; Squacky's afraid of the dark, so the Pajanimals turn to the moon for help.
episodes.title: A Colorful Problem / Light in the Sky

episodes.synopsis: Apollo's birthday is tomorrow, but Cowbella doesn't feel like attending; Sweetpea Sue is bothered by loud noises, especially a thunderstorm at night.
episodes.title: Apollo's Special Day / Night Will Sing Us To Sleep

episodes.synopsis: Squacky gets addicted to a handheld video game, creating problems for all; Cowbella eats too much candy and has trouble falling asleep.
episodes.title: Game Day / Super Sweet Night

episodes.synopsis: Apollo is tall enough for the rocket ride at the fun park, but his friends aren't; Cowbella's worried about having a nightmare and plans not to sleep.
episodes.title: The Rocket Ride / Dream a Happy Dream

episodes.synopsis: Sweetpea Sue is nervous about sharing Daisy Puff on Share Day; Apollo's had a bad day, so the Pajanimals all visit the Moon to help him feel better.
episodes.title: Share Day / Tomorrow Is a Brand New Day

episodes.synopsis: The Pajanimals must take care of Fluffy the dog for a day; Squacky won't get his ball from under the bed -- he thinks there's a monster under there.
episodes.title: Puppy Love / Under the Bed

episodes.synopsis: Squacky is scared of the outdoors and doesn't want to go outside; the Pajanimals are going on a trip, and Sweetpea Sue's worried about leaving home.
episodes.title: Not-So-Great Outdoors / Home Sweet Home
